,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":2560,"height":1440,"file_path":"/3mxteiwtcCPjbYKlyC0WxY1G9J3.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":4,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":2.278},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/zxoCBPLrDPlyfOBjrlXmpv5YAvz.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":4,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/z7Mdw4vuccQ2PvuXIz76s3kEKeT.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/XVgfwrN1XvZUj9m0tSPC97gyCk.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/gkQR0jC4EHDxD5X0n0Vdn5YT9ns.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/nyw3vKjzoBSC0G1GUhbwq2BxUOW.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/jnOP2fVcL8ZD2BcOQCpuDp9FBOe.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/1gRowHT9D7fzumK6NLlnWidjvr.jpg","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":2560,"height":1440,"file_path":"/sDsbHhRHSB5Dy1vidydW3JBRsDv.jpg","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":2560,"height":1440,"file_path":"/orw7g8WELQgtCJ8IYqOpQDfCCyW.jpg","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/zQmWGT8THPkejaMe5H8EmokHjgX.jpg","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/ecbQOvPHJguQcIsLjeeHyPww2L9.jpg","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":2600,"height":1463,"file_path":"/4yNmiOoTlxYCgGipWjpsbLZsxKA.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.777,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-25T03:43:28.759+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"The Lives of Others","runtime":137,"tagline":"Before the Fall of the Berlin Wall, East Germany's Secret Police Listened to Your Secrets.","homepage":"","overview":"In 1984 East Berlin, dedicated Stasi officer Gerd Wiesler begins spying on a famous playwright and his actress-lover Christa-Maria. Wiesler becomes unexpectedly sympathetic to the couple, and faces conflicting loyalties when his superior takes a liking to Christa-Maria."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":137,"tagline":"In einem System der Macht ist nichts privat.","homepage":"","overview":"Ost-Berlin, November 1984. Fünf Jahre vor seinem Ende sichert der DDR-Staat seinen Machtanspruch mit einem erbarmungslosen System aus Kontrolle und Überwachung. Als Oberstleutnant Anton Grubitz den linientreuen Stasi-Hauptmann Gerd Wiesler auf den erfolgreichen Dramatiker Georg Dreyman und seine Lebensgefährtin, den Theaterstar Christa-Maria Sieland, ansetzt, verspricht er sich davon einen Karriereschub. Immerhin stehen höchste politische Kreise hinter dem „operativen Vorgang“. Womit er nicht gerechnet hat: Das intime Eindringen in die Welt der Observierten verändert auch den Spitzel. Das Eintauchen in „das Leben der Anderen“ – in Liebe, Literatur, freies Denken und Reden – macht Wiesler die Armseligkeit seines eigenen Daseins bewusst und eröffnet ihm eine nie gekannte Welt, der er sich immer weniger entziehen kann. Doch das System ist nicht mehr zu stoppen – ein gefährliches Spiel beginnt."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"A mások élete","runtime":137,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Kelet-Berlin, 1983 novembere, hat évvel a berlini fal leomlása előtt: az NDK és állambiztonsági szolgálata még elnyomja a (másként) gondolkodókat, és kíméletlen megfigyelő-besúgó rendszere mindenkit behálóz. Ennek a gépezetnek tökéletes fogaskereke Gerd Wiesler százados (Ulrich Mühe), akit politikai nyomásra egy sikeres színpadi szerzőre, Georg Dreymanra (Sebastian Koch) és élettársára, az ünnepelt színésznőre Christa-Maria Sielandra (Martina Gedeck) állítanak. A rendszerhez vakon hű Wiesler, a mások életét figyelve hamarosan ráébred saját élete kisszerűségére."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"La vida de los otros","runtime":137,"tagline":"Hasta que cayó el muro, la Stasi escuchaba tus secretos.","homepage":"","overview":"El capitán Gerd Wiesler (Ulrich Mühe) es un oficial extremadamente competente de la Stasi, la todopoderosa policía secreta del régimen comunista de la antigua República Democrática Alemana. Pero, cuando en 1984 le encomiendan que espíe a la pareja formada por el prestigioso escritor Georg Dreyman (Sebastian Koch) y la popular actriz Christa-Maria Sieland (Martina Gedenk), no sabe hasta qué punto esa misión va a influir en su propia vida..."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"La Vie des autres","runtime":137,"tagline":"Où le pouvoir est absolu, rien est privé.","homepage":"","overview":"Au début des années 1980, en Allemagne de l'Est, l'auteur à succès Georges Dreyman et sa compagne, l'actrice Christa-Maria Sieland, sont considérés comme faisant partie de l'élite des intellectuels de l’État communiste, même si, secrètement, ils n'adhèrent aux idées du parti. Le Ministère de la Culture commence à s'intéresser à Christa et dépêche un agent secret, nommé Wiesler, ayant pour mission de l'observer. Tandis qu'il progresse dans l'enquête, le couple d'intellectuels le fascine de plus en plus…"},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":137,"tagline":"HGW XX/7","homepage":"","overview":"Oost Berlijn, 1984. Glasnost is nog heel ver weg, de bevolking wordt onderdrukt door de Oost-Duitse geheime politie (Stasi). De Stasi wordt alom gezien als een van de meest effectieve inlichtingendiensten ter wereld. Het doel van de Stasi: alles te weten komen. De succesvolle toneelschrijver Georg Dreyman (Sebastian Koch) en zijn geliefde, de actrice Christa-Maria Sieland (Martina Gedeck), zijn sterren in de DDR. Maar hun acties en vooral gedachten zijn niet altijd in lijn met de ideologie van de socialistische heilstaat. De minister van Cultuur is erg geïnteresseerd in Christa-Maria en geeft Stasi-agent Wiesler (Ulrich Mühe), alias HGW XX/7, opdracht de twee af te luisteren. Boven hun appartement, op zolder, luistert hij dag en nacht hun leven af. Maar hoe meer hij in hun leven wordt gezogen, des te meer moeite heeft hij zijn loyaliteit aan de staat te behouden."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Başkalarının Hayatı","runtime":137,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Doğu Almanya'nın kapalı politik atmosferi içinde, partiye ve devlete sadakatleri sürekli sorgulanan insanlar, daimi bir baskı altındadırlar. Gerd Wiesler de, ünlü oyun yazarı Georg Dreyman'ı gözlemlemekle görevlendirilmiş bir yüzbaşıdır. Yazar ve sevgilisinin yaşadıkları apartmanın çatı katına yerleşen Yüzbaşı, sürekli olarak ikilinin yaşamını Bakan Hempf'e rapor etmektedir. Uzun bir süre herhangi bir olumsuzluk rapor edemez. Ta ki Bakan Hempf, Georg Dreyman'ın kız arkadaşına cinsel tacizde bulunana kadar. Sevgilisinin maruz kaldığı durum üzerine yaşadığı baskı ile ilgili sabrı taşan Georg, Doğu Almanya'daki koşulları tüm dünyanın duyması için Der Spiegel'e yazı yazmaya karar verir. Yüzbaşı için aradığı fırsat sonunda doğmuştur. Ama günler boyu izlediği bu iki insanın hayatının kendi üzerinde bıraktığı etkiler, hayatını ve varoluşunu sorgulamasına neden olacaktır. Katıldığı pek çok festivalde ödüle boğulan Başkalarının Hayatı, etkili anlatımı ve hümanist yaklaşımı ile dikkat çekiyor."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"窃听风暴","runtime":0,"tagline":"柏林墙没倒的时候，东德的秘密警察听过了你的秘密","homepage":"","overview":"一部政治惊悚片，亦是一曲人性剧，本片的故事始于1984年的东柏林，时值柏林墙倒塌与“公开性”政策实施五年前，并最终将我们带至1991年已然统一的德国。影片刻画了东德全权秘密警察机构史塔西麾下的精锐军官——格尔德·维泽勒上尉逐渐醒悟的过程。[索尼影业经典]"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Le vite degli altri","runtime":137,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nei primi anni Ottanta, il drammaturgo di successo Georg Dreyman e la sua compagna di sempre, la famosa attrice Christa-Maria Sieland, si trasferiscono a Berlino Est. I due sono considerati dalla DDR tra i più importanti intellettuali del regime comunista e sono tenuti in grande considerazione, malgrado in cuor loro Georg e Christa-Maria non siano sempre allineati con la linea del partito. Un giorno il ministro della cultura assiste ad uno spettacolo dell'attrice e se ne innamora. Chiede allora a Gerd Wiesler, uno dei più valorosi agenti della Stasi, di avvicinare la coppia, conoscerla meglio, ed osservare ogni loro spostamento e interesse. Sarà la vita di Gerd ad essere cambiata dal rapporto con lo scrittore."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Жизнь других","runtime":0,"tagline":"У вас нет права хранить молчание","homepage":"","overview":"Восточный Берлин, ноябрь 1984 года. За пять лет до своего низвержения восточно-германское правительство обеспечивает свои притязания на власть беспощадной системой контроля и сыска. Преданный партиец капитан Герд Вислер надеется подняться по служебной лестнице, выполняя работу по сбору улик против драматурга Георга Дрaймана и его подруги - знаменитой театральной актрисы Кристы-Марии Зиланд.\r Однако он не ожидал, что погружение в мир объекта наблюдения меняет и самого сыскного агента. Погружение в жизнь других - в любовь, литературу, свободу мысли и слова - приводит Вислера к острому осознанию скудости его собственного существования и открывает ему совершенно новый образ жизни, противостоять которому становится всё сложнее. Но когда система уже запущена, она не может быть остановлена. Опасная игра началась…"},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"As Vidas dos Outros","runtime":137,"tagline":"Nada é Privado. Nada é Sagrado.","homepage":"","overview":"No início dos anos 80, na antiga RDA, o bem sucedido dramaturgo Georg, e a sua companheira de muitos anos Christa, uma famosa actriz, são duas das grandes estrelas intelectuais do estado socialista, apesar de, em privado, não concordarem com tudo o que o partido faz. O Ministro da Cultura que começa a interessar-se por Christa, manda um agente secreto espiar o casal. O agente encarregue da tarefa começa a interessar-se profundamente na vida do casal."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Życie na podsłuchu","runtime":137,"tagline":"Więcej władzy. Mniej prywatności.","homepage":"","overview":"Film porusza wciąż gorący temat służb specjalnych. Opisuje przerażającą, paranoiczną i czasami śmieszną historię systemu kontroli obywateli we wschodnich Niemczech. Historia oparta na faktach. Wczesne lata 80-te. Znany dramaturg Georg Dreyman wraz ze swoją partnerką Christą, popularną aktorką tworzą parę intelektualistów- gwiazd w socjalistycznym państwie. Ich poglądy i styl życia nie zawsze zgadzają się z doktryną partii dlatego są pod ścisłą obserwacją Agenta Stasi, którego zaczyna wciągać i fascynować ich życie..."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"De andras liv","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Filmen utspelar sig i Östberlin, huvudsakligen 1984 och 1985, och handlar om den till synes känslolöse Stasi-mannen Gerd Wiesler, som får i uppdrag att övervaka författaren Georg Dreyman och dennes flickvän, skådespelerskan Christa-Maria Sieland. Inledningsvis ser Wiesler uppdraget som en möjlighet att klättra i hierarkin och rapporterar sanningsenligt till sina överhuvuden i Stasi-ledningen. Ganska snart, då fascinationen för och förståelsen för de övervakade konstnärerna växer, flyttas hans lojalitet och utan deras vetskap börjar han istället att skydda dem. Men hur länge kan han skydda dem och till vilket pris?"},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Životy těch druhých","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Rok 1984. Do pádu obávaného režimu ve Východním Německu zbývá necelých šest let. Vládnoucí Jednotná socialistická strana upevňuje svou pozici pomocí nemilosrdného systému monitorování a manipulace s potenciálně nebezpečnými lidmi, k čemuž využívá tajnou policii Stasi. Věrný stoupenec režimu, kapitán Gerd Wiesler (Ulrich Mühe), se ve snaze o kariérní postup pustí do shromažďování kompromitujících důkazů proti známému divadelnímu dramatikovi Georgi Dreymanovi (Sebastian Koch) a jeho atraktivní přítelkyni Christě-Marii Sieland (Martina Gedeck), která krátce předtím učarovala mocnému ministrovi kultury (Thomas Thieme). Jakmile se však do světa dvou divadelních hvězd ponoří, začne být jejich životy fascinován a uvědomí si omezenost své vlastní existence."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"Живот других","runtime":137,"tagline":"Живот других","homepage":"","overview":"Радња филма смештеног у источни Берлин 1984. године прати Герда Вислера, искусног службеника државне безбедности, који добија задатак да прислушкује познатог и успешног позоришног писца Георга Дрејмана. Ово дебитантско целовечерње остварење редитеља Флоријана Хенкела фон Донерсмарка имало је рекордних 11 номинација на додели Немачких националних филмских награда, а овенчан је Оскаром за најбољи страни филм 2007. године."},"name":"Srpski","iso_639_1":"sr","iso_3166_1":"RS","english_name":"Serbian"},{"data":{"title":"De andres liv","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Østberlin, 1984. Den dybt loyale Stasi-Agent Wiesler. er fra højeste sted blevet beordret om at overvåge den intellektuelle forfatter Dreyman, og hans kæreste, Sieland, en kendt skuespillerinde, men finder snart ud af at ministeren kun søger snavs på Dreyman for selv at kunne få fingre i kæresten. Wiesler bliver mere og mere fascineret af deres liv, og bliver trukket længere ind end han burde."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"타인의 삶","runtime":0,"tagline":"난 그들의 삶을 훔쳤고 그들은 나의 인생을 바꿨다","homepage":"","overview":"1980년대 중반 동독에서는 9만명이 넘는 비밀경찰(슈타지)과 약 17만명의 정보원이 활동했다. 만인에 대한 만인의 밀고로 유지되는 세계에서는 더 끈덕지게 의심하는 자가 유능한 멤버다. 주인공 게르트 비즐러(울리히 뮈헤)는 탁월한 감시 및 심문 실력과 정치적 신념으로 무장한 비밀경찰. 비즐러는 동독 최고의 극작가 드라이만과 그의 애인이자 인기 여배우 크리스타를 감시하는 중대 임무를 맡는다. 그러나 시간이 지날수록 드라이만을 체포할 만한 단서는 찾을 수 없다. 비즐러는 오히려 드라이만과 크리스타의 삶으로 인해 감동받고 사랑을 느끼며 이전의 삶과는 달리 인간적인 모습으로 변화하기 시작하는데..."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"חיים של אחרים","runtime":137,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"זוכה 7 פרסי האוסקר הגרמני לשנת 2006 - כולל הבימוי, השחקן, שחקן המשנה והתסריט הטובים ביותר. זוכה 3 פרסי האוסקר האירופאי לשנת 2006 - כולל תסריט, סרט ושחקן. מועמד לגלובוס הזהב 2006 - לסרט הזר הטוב ביותר. ג'ורג' וקריסטינה-מאריה הם זוג אינטלקטואלים נוצץ במזרח גרמניה של ראשית שנות השמונים לפני נפילת החומה. הוא מחזאי ואיש רוח מוכשר והיא שחקנית מצליחה. ויזלר הוא סוכן מיוחד שמונה לעקוב אחר חייהם ולוודא שהם \"נאמנים למפלגה\". הוא לא שיער שחייו ישתנו ללא היכר מרגע שיתחיל ה-\"מבצע\" והוא יכנס לחייהם. ויזלר מוצא עצמו מפתח בחשאי אמפתיה וההערצה כלפי בני הזוג ואורח חייהם. היחשפותו לשירה, לחופש הכתיבה וליצירה שלהם, מביאים אותו להתבונן מחדש בחייו. ויזלר נפתח אל עולם אחר לגמרי, אותו הקפיד תמיד להרחיק מעליו."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Οι Ζωές των Άλλων","runtime":137,"tagline":"Όταν η εξουσία είναι απόλυτη, τίποτα δεν είναι ιδιωτικό","homepage":"","overview":"1984. Η Ανατολική Γερμανία βρίσκεται για τα καλά εγκλωβισμένη μέσα στο θεοσκότεινο τούνελ, που την έχουν οδηγήσει οι ακραίες ορέξεις του απολυταρχικού καθεστώτος και οι απάνθρωπες κινήσεις των μυστικών υπηρεσιών, δίχως να διαφαίνεται κάποιο φως σε κάποια από τις άκρες του. Ο πράκτορας Γκερντ Βίσλερ, λαμβάνει την εντολή από τον διοικητή του Ταξίαρχος Γκρούμπιτζ, να οργανώσει επιχείρηση παρακολούθησης ενός από τους πιο αναγνωρισμένους συγγραφείς της χώρας, του Γκιοργκ Ντράιμαν, του οποίου οι φιλοκυβερνητικές πεποιθήσεις έχουν τεθεί εν αμφιβόλω. Εκείνος όμως έχοντας πλήρη άγνοια για τις ορέξεις της Στάζι, παρακινούμενος από τον βάναυσο τρόπο διακυβέρνησης του Χόνεκερ, επιθυμεί να αποστείλει στην Δύση, ένα κείμενο μανιφέστο για την αντιδημοκρατική λειτουργία της πατρίδας του."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"Животът на другите","runtime":137,"tagline":"Преди падането на берлинската стена, полицията в Източна Германия подслушваше тайните Ви.","homepage":"","overview":"Източен Берлин, ноември 1984. Пет години преди упадъка си, някогашното правителство на Източна Германия осигурява властта си чрез безмилостна система от контрол и наблюдение. Лоялният капитан Вайслер се надява да подпомогне кариерата си, като приеме задачата да събира доказателства срещу драматурга Дрейман и неговата приятелка, известната актриса Криста-Мария Зиланд. Това, което Вайслер не е очаквал, е, че потапяйки се в света на своята „мишена”, той започва да се променя. Любовта, литературата, свободомислието и свободата на словото разкриват на Вайслер колко незначителен е собственият му живот."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"Viețile altora","runtime":137,"tagline":"Înainte de căderea zidului Berlinului, poliția secretă a Germaniei de Est asculta secretele tale.","homepage":"","overview":"Un ofițer de securitate est-german primește misiunea de a spiona un dramaturg bănuit de planuri subversive la adresa regimului comunist. În scurt timp, sensibilul și meticulosul securist va fi pur și simplu fascinat de lumea ce i se descoperă prin intermediul microfoanelor care împânzesc casa scriitorului. Dar, odată pornit, teribilul sistem de opresiune nu mai poate fi oprit. A început un joc periculos, în care nu există intimitate, în care nu mai există nimic sacru, în care totul este posibil."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Життя інших","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Оповідання фільму розвертається у Східному Берліні в 1984 році - за 5 років до падіння Берлінської стіни. Агент \"штазі\" Герд Візлер, відданий соціалістичним ідеалам висококласний спеціаліст, засумнівався у благонадійності тетрального драматурга Георга Дреймана і за завданням полковника Грубітца поставив на прослухування його квартиру. Незабаром Візлер, що дістав доступ до чужого життя, проникається симпатією до людини, за якою вимушений стежити з ранку до ночі..."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"A Vida dos Outros","runtime":138,"tagline":"Antes da queda do Muro de Berlim, a polícia secreta da Alemanha Oriental ouvia seus segredos.","homepage":"","overview":"Georg Dreyman é o maior dramaturgo da Alemanha Oriental, sendo por muitos considerado o modelo perfeito de cidadão para o país, já que não contesta o governo nem seu regime político. Apesar disto o ministro Bruno Hempf acha por bem acompanhar seus passos, para descobrir se Dreyman tem algo a esconder. Ele passa esta tarefa para Anton Grubitz, que a princípio não vê nada de errado com Dreyman mas é alertado por Gerd Wiesler, seu subordinado, de que ele deveria ser vigiado. Grubitz passa a tarefa a Wiesler, que monta uma estrutura em que Dreyman e sua namorada, a atriz Christa-Maria Sieland, são vigiados 24 horas."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Življenje drugih","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Le pet let pred padcem berlinskega zidu spremljamo zadnje vzdihljaje represivnega sistema v Vzhodni Nemčiji, kjer nihče ni varen pred zloglasno obveščevalno policijo Stasi. Komisar Wiesler dobi navodilo, naj prične prisluškovati znanemu gledališkemu režiserju in njegovi spremljevalki, a počasi odkrije, da pravi vzrok za nadzorovanje tiči povsem drugod. Vpogled v drobne življenjske radosti in strahove drugih ljudi na glavo obrne tudi njegovo lastno razmišljanje. Dramo je evropska filmska akademija nagradila v kategorijah najboljšega filma, igralca in scenarija, prejel pa je tudi oskarjevo nominacijo za najboljši tujejezični film."},"name":"Slovenščina","iso_639_1":"sl","iso_3166_1":"SI","english_name":"Slovenian"},{"data":{"title":"Muiden elämä","runtime":137,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Käsikirjoittaja Georg Dreyman ja suosittu näyttelijä Christa-Maria Sieland ovat älykkäitä tähtiä, jotka elävät sosialistisessa yhteiskunnassa. Mutta he eivät aina ajattele ja käyttäydy maan poliittisen järjestelmän sallimalla tavalla. Eräänä päivänä kulttuuriministeriö kiinnostuu Christasta ja panee Stasi-agentti Wieslerin salakuuntelemaan heidän asuntoaan. Ajan mittaan Wiesler kiinnostuu heidän elämästään."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"善き人のためのソナタ","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"シュタージ（国家保安省）の局員ヴィースラー（ウルリッヒ・ミューエ）は、劇作家のドライマン（セバスチャン・コッホ）と恋人で舞台女優のクリスタ（マルティナ・ゲデック）が反体制的であるという証拠をつかむよう命じられる。ヴィースラーは盗聴器を通して彼らの監視を始めるが、自由な思想を持つ彼らに次第に魅せられ……。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"竊聽風暴","runtime":137,"tagline":"秘密！權力！致命的背叛！","homepage":"","overview":"1984年柏林圍牆倒塌前5年，東德國家安全局「史塔西」正以恐怖威權控制著人民。著名劇作家德瑞曼被懷疑撰寫反動文章。於是，秘密警察衛斯勒奉命全天候監控德瑞曼和女友－知名女伶西蘭的生活，期望能找出關鍵證據。然而不知不覺中，衛斯勒逐步融入兩人多姿的生活。他不僅對德瑞曼產生了友誼，更分享了兩人之間的愛情與爭執、秘密與謊言…，而德瑞曼和西蘭卻渾然不覺。當德瑞曼和西蘭出現嫌隙，衛斯勒奉命逼供西蘭。西蘭會出賣德瑞曼嗎？衛斯勒能找出證據嗎？德瑞曼又能成功躲過這場風暴嗎？一場驚險卻精彩的政治、情報、藝術與愛情的角力，自此展開…。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Životy tých druhých","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Rok 1984. Do pádu režimu v NDR zostáva necelých šesť rokov. Vládnuca Jednotná socialistická strana upevňuje svoju pozíciu pomocou nemilosrdného systému monitorovania a manipulácie s potenciálne nebezpečnými ľuďmi, k čomu využíva tajnú políciu Stasi. Verný stúpenec režimu, kapitán Gerd Wiesler, je ministrom kultúry poverený zhromažďovaním kompromitujúcich dôkazov proti známemu divadelnému dramatikovi Georgi Dreymanovi a jeho atraktívnej priateľke, herečke Christe-Marii Sieland. Dôvod je ale prozaický - minister sa do krásnej herečky zamiloval. Akonáhle sa však Wiesler do sveta dvoch divadelných hviezd ponorí, začne byť ich životmi fascinovaný a uvedomí si obmedzenosť svojej vlastnej existencie. Preto začína tejto dvojici pomáhať a kryje ich protištátnu činnosť. Weislerov šéf ale Christu napriek všetkému zatýka a donúti ju k spolupráci a donášaniu na jej partnera. Pád Berlínskeho múru sa ale blíži ..."},"name":"Slovenčina","iso_639_1":"sk","iso_3166_1":"SK","english_name":"Slovak"},{"data":{"title":"De andres liv","runtime":137,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Noen år før det sosialistiske regimet i Øst-Tyskland rakner, er det fryktede Stasi i stand til å overvåke og etterforske hvem som helst for hva som helst. En effektiv Stasi-offiser får for første gang sympati for dem han skal avlytte. Men kan han utgjøre en forskjell?"},"name":"Norsk","iso_639_1":"no","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian"},{"data":{"title":"La vida de los otros","runtime":138,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"En 1984, en Berlín Oriental, un agente de la policía secreta, que vigilaba a un escritor y a su amante, se encuentra cada vez más absorto por sus vidas."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"حياة الأخرين","runtime":0,"tagline":"قبل سقوط جدار برلين ، استمعت الشرطة السرية في ألمانيا الشرقية إلى أسرارك.","homepage":"","overview":"قصة حب مأساوية تدور أحداثها في برلين الشرقية على خلفية ثقافة سرية خاضعة لسيطرة ستاسي. أمر كابتن Stasi Wieler بمراقبة المؤلف Dreyman والأنغماس بشكل أعمق وأعمق في حياته حتى يصل إلى عتبة الشك في النظام."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"Khoảnh Khắc Cuộc Đời","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Đông Đức tháng 11, 1984. Wiesler là nhân viên Stasi chuyên theo dõi người khác. Điệp vụ mới nhất của hắn là nghe trộm hàng ngày hoạt động của cặp nghệ sĩ Sieland và Dreyman. Từ sự quan sát cuộc sống của những người khác, Wiesler đã có những biến chuyển tâm lý rõ rệt để dẫn đến thay đổi cuộc sống của chính mình."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Život drugih","runtime":0,"tagline":"Prije pada Berlinskog zida, tajna policija Istočne Njemačke slušala je tvoje tajne.","homepage":"","overview":"Istočni Berlin, sredina osamdesetih godina. Georg Dreyman poznati je istočnonjemački pisac i dramatičar, oženjen poznatom kazališnom glumicom Christom-Mariom. Jednoga dana poznati agent Stasija, Wiesler, dobiva naredbu da špijunira spomenuti par zbog najave da su protudržavni agenti."},"name":"Hrvatski","iso_639_1":"hr","iso_3166_1":"HR","english_name":"Croatian"},{"data":{"title":"竊聽者","runtime":137,"tagline":"是迫害異己的呈堂證供 亦是精神交流的互動記錄 在竊聽生命的同時 一個秘密警察 真的....良心發現?!","homepage":"","overview":"一個政府秘密特工、一個極具才華的劇作家、一位美艷女星。  秘密警察韋斯勒上尉，活在封閉的體制下，每天只為政府工作，將真相埋藏。劇作家基約‧戴文身處滿佈線眼的世界裡，但以維護公義為己任，朝思暮想希望將事實公諸於世。女星姬絲‧斯蘭面對複雜的人生，甚麼也不想知，只想安份守己地過日子，祈盼在別人懷裡找到安穩的感覺。  三人走在一起，令衝突一觸即發，各人應樣怎樣自處？公義、愛情、生命到底哪樣比較脆弱？"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"La vida dels altres","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Català","iso_639_1":"ca","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Catalan"},{"data":{"title":"სხვების ცხოვრება","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ასი ათასი თანამშრომელი, ორასი ათასი ინფორმატორი. ისინი ერთად არიან პარტიის ფარი და ხმალი, ცნობილი შტაზის. მათი მეთოდი ეჭვია. სხვების ცხოვრება მათი პროფესიაა. პოპულარული მწერალი და დრამატურგი გეორგ დრეიმანი სიცოცხლის ბოლომდე იცოცხლებდა, მადლიერი მკითხველების ყურადღების მიღმა და აბსოლუტურად უინტერესო სპეცსამსახურებისთვის, რომ არა ცნობილ თეატრის მსახიობთან რომანი. ძალიან ცნობილი, რომ ცენტრალური კომიტეტის გავლენიანი ჩინოვნიკისთვის შეუმჩნეველი დარჩეს. ასე ჩნდებიან დრეიმანის ცხოვრებაში შტაზის სპეციალისტები."},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"Kitų gyvenimai","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Už lango 1984-ieji. Iki Berlyno sienos griūties liko penkeri pavojingo ir baisaus gyvenimo metai. Vos ne kiekvieną Rytų Vokietijos piliečių žingsnį kontroliuoja 100 tūkst. negailestingų slaptosios policijos Stasi agentų ir dar 200 tūkst. savanorių skundikų, kurie siekia žinoti absoliučiai viską apie kitų žmonių gyvenimus. Saugumui ištikimai tarnaujantis kapitonas Gerdas Viesleris dėl darbo aukoja asmeninį gyvenimą. Jis šventai tiki socialistiniais idealais, sugeba užuosti disidentus per tūkstantį žingsnių ir žino geriausius būdus išgauti informaciją. Kai ministro kėdėje įsitaisęs buvęs kolega Hempfas paprašo atidžiau stebėti neva įtartiną populiaraus rašytojo Georgo Dreimano elgesį, Gerdas Viesleris jo bute įtaiso daugybę \"blakių\" ir pradeda klausytis vyriškio pokalbių."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"},{"data":{"title":"วิกฤติรักแดนเบอร์ลิน","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ในไม่กี่ปี ก่อนกำแพงเบอร์ลินจะพังทลาย ในยุคนั้น ผู้ที่รัฐบาลจ้องจับผิดจะไร้ซึ่งเสรีภาพส่วนบุคคล แม้กระทั่งจอร์จ เดรย์แมน กับนักแสดงสาว คริสต้า มาเรีย ซีแลนด์ ที่ถูกลอบสังเกตุการณ์และดักฟัง โดยมีคำสั่งมาจากรัฐมนตรีบรูโน เฮมพฟ์ ซึ่งหาข้ออ้างเรื่องการสงสัยในการจงรักภักดีของเดรย์แมน ที่มีต่อพรรคสังคมนิยมหรือเอสอีดี ที่เป็นผู้ปกครองประเทศเยอรมนีอยู่"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Oost Berlijn, 1984. Glasnost is nog heel ver weg, de bevolking wordt onderdrukt door de Oost-Duitse geheime politie (Stasi). De Stasi wordt alom gezien als een van de meest effectieve inlichtingendiensten ter wereld. Het doel van de Stasi: alles te weten komen. De succesvolle toneelschrijver Georg Dreyman (Sebastian Koch) en zijn geliefde, de actrice Christa-Maria Sieland (Martina Gedeck), zijn sterren in de DDR. Maar hun acties en vooral gedachten zijn niet altijd in lijn met de ideologie van de socialistische heilstaat. De minister van Cultuur is erg geïnteresseerd in Christa-Maria en geeft Stasi-agent Wiesler (Ulrich Mühe), alias HGW XX/7, opdracht de twee af te luisteren. Boven hun appartement, op zolder, luistert hij dag en nacht hun leven af. Maar hoe meer hij in hun leven wordt gezogen, des te meer moeite heeft hij zijn loyaliteit aan de staat te behouden."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"BE","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"La Vie des autres","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Dans les années 1980, un officier de la Stasi est de plus en plus fasciné par le couple d'artistes est-berlinois qu'il est chargé d'épier."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"65a2bc38b7b69d01253c0381","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/65a2bc38b7b69d01253c0381","author":"portman123","content":"Good guys facing tragic circumstances in an interesting period of history. \r\n\r\nBecause you view the main characters lives from the perspective of the morally confused Stasi Officer investigating them, you receive more information than the characters have about their hopeless situation. This makes it all the more tragic to see the suffering they endure. \r\n\r\nAbsolutely love this film. The only film so far to make my dad and I cry.","created_at":"2024-01-13T16:37:12.879Z","updated_at":"2024-01-16T15:27:19.799Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":10,"username":"portman123","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"663f36aa93715248189b1270","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/663f36aa93715248189b1270","author":"CinemaSerf","content":"$11","created_at":"2024-05-11T09:13:14.798Z","updated_at":"2024-05-13T09:02:33.070Z","author_details":{"name":"CinemaSerf","rating":7,"username":"Geronimo1967","avatar_path":"/9HcQx0Yfbxy8eqr3ft66X9uWMf0.jpg"}}],"recommendations":[{"id":25376,"adult":false,"title":"The Secret in Their Eyes","video":false,"overview":"Hoping to put to rest years of unease concerning a past case, retired criminal investigator Benjamín begins writing a novel based on the unsolved mystery of a newlywed’s rape and murder. With the help of a former colleague, judge Irene, he attempts to make sense of the past.","genre_ids":[9648,53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.0422,"vote_count":2788,"poster_path":"/dkeAwfZzwL3WvToydE3CXiY80E0.jpg","release_date":"2009-08-13","vote_average":7.976,"backdrop_path":"/fNHCogWhABNAmzk0IFdzQP5XLYj.jpg","original_title":"El secreto de sus ojos","original_language":"es"},{"id":613,"adult":false,"title":"Downfall","video":false,"overview":"In April of 1945, Germany stands at the brink of defeat with the Russian Army closing in from the east and the Allied Expeditionary Force attacking from the west. In Berlin, capital of the Third Reich, Adolf Hitler proclaims that Germany will still achieve victory and orders his generals and advisers to fight to the last man. When the end finally does come, and Hitler lies dead by his own hand, what is left of his military must find a way to end the killing that is the Battle of Berlin, and lay down their arms in surrender.","genre_ids":[18,36,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.0459,"vote_count":4200,"poster_path":"/cP1ElGjBhbZAAqmueXjHDKlSwiP.jpg","release_date":"2004-09-16","vote_average":7.857,"backdrop_path":"/cT80aGpjWZLn8rd7cLtsbktFMhf.jpg","original_title":"Der Untergang","original_language":"de"},{"id":338,"adult":false,"title":"Good Bye, Lenin!","video":false,"overview":"Alex Kerner's mother was in a coma while the Berlin wall fell. When she wakes up he must try to keep her from learning what happened (as she was an avid communist supporter) to avoid shocking her which could lead to another heart attack.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3687,"vote_count":2578,"poster_path":"/uHk1oGEbnvQGLnyiiYxTslZLoog.jpg","release_date":"2003-02-13","vote_average":7.538,"backdrop_path":"/uBLmfG7MyNXPXI50eMs1ZjxpbnV.jpg","original_title":"Good Bye, Lenin!","original_language":"de"},{"id":935,"adult":false,"title":"Dr. Strangelove or: How I Learned to Stop Worrying and Love the Bomb","video":false,"overview":"After the insane General Jack D. Ripper initiates a nuclear strike on the Soviet Union, a war room full of politicians, generals and a Russian diplomat all frantically try to stop it.","genre_ids":[35,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.4877,"vote_count":6037,"poster_path":"/6x7MzQ6BOMlRzam1StcmPO9v61g.jpg","release_date":"1964-01-29","vote_average":8.1,"backdrop_path":"/7i0L2ee4Iy0aXV6vR5u1ZmblOrx.jpg","original_title":"Dr. Strangelove or: How I Learned to Stop Worrying and Love the Bomb","original_language":"en"},{"id":4836,"adult":false,"title":"Layer Cake","video":false,"overview":"When a seemingly straight-forward drug deal goes awry, XXXX has to break his die-hard rules and turn up the heat, not only to outwit the old regime and come out on top, but to save his own skin...","genre_ids":[18,53,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.2061,"vote_count":2310,"poster_path":"/rDOxXteqxALBaSa3V3zTjGJuyWB.jpg","release_date":"2004-09-30","vote_average":6.911,"backdrop_path":"/a8230eNW59hSOkj5XrRpzMMh0WT.jpg","original_title":"Layer Cake","original_language":"en"},{"id":762,"adult":false,"title":"Monty Python and the Holy Grail","video":false,"overview":"King Arthur, accompanied by his squire, recruits his Knights of the Round Table, including Sir Bedevere the Wise, Sir Lancelot the Brave, Sir Robin the Not-Quite-So-Brave-As-Sir-Lancelot and Sir Galahad the Pure. On the way, Arthur battles the Black Knight who, despite having had all his limbs chopped off, insists he can still fight. They reach Camelot, but Arthur decides not  to enter, as \"it is a silly place\".","genre_ids":[12,35,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.7378,"vote_count":6268,"poster_path":"/7nTkHjETdGMYK1phHwDbPsrzbYl.jpg","release_date":"1975-04-03","vote_average":7.802,"backdrop_path":"/1KgXxv6tHXOnakqYvMPvFwYKWiw.jpg","original_title":"Monty Python and the Holy Grail","original_language":"en"},{"id":9277,"adult":false,"title":"The Sting","video":false,"overview":"A novice con man teams up with an acknowledged master to avenge the murder of a mutual friend by pulling off the ultimate big con and swindling a fortune from a big-time mobster.","genre_ids":[35,80,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.5622,"vote_count":2879,"poster_path":"/ckmYng37zey8INYf6d10cVgIG93.jpg","release_date":"1973-12-25","vote_average":8,"backdrop_path":"/1r9lH3DaSWKGyvZaoo6BF5STOk5.jpg","original_title":"The Sting","original_language":"en"},{"id":1583,"adult":false,"title":"Lammbock","video":false,"overview":"Stefan and Kai run a thriving business: a home-grown cannabis trade disguised as a pizza delivery service. For now they just have to fight aphids.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3344,"vote_count":223,"poster_path":"/z1AeFrBKkdZBUi4YvP7TsaQ7zoe.jpg","release_date":"2001-08-23","vote_average":6.899,"backdrop_path":"/vK0KkUP57W4N8CtbSaRlqXXjXIz.jpg","original_title":"Lammbock","original_language":"de"},{"id":130739,"adult":false,"title":"A Coffee in Berlin","video":false,"overview":"Niko, a twenty-something college dropout, lives for the moment as he drifts through the streets of Berlin, curiously observing everyone around him and oblivious to his growing status as an outsider. Then on one fateful day, through a series of absurdly amusing encounters, everything changes.","genre_ids":[18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6394,"vote_count":347,"poster_path":"/gy58pmCztFrpxaRM9rGhv93LgCP.jpg","release_date":"2012-11-01","vote_average":7.196,"backdrop_path":"/xL10TJ5dQluARc6Qq1dkHs2Xrk1.jpg","original_title":"Oh Boy","original_language":"de"},{"id":308980,"adult":false,"title":"Zero Point","video":false,"overview":"Sensitive and restless Johannes is accepted to an elite school in Tallinn and expects life to go uphill. Instead, he becomes the victim of mental abuse by his classmates. In search of recognition, he goes to his old Lasnamäe friends, who spend their time doing drugs, hanging around, and partying, rather than focusing on schoolwork. At home, Johannes must deal with his mother’s deteriorating mental health. As the tension grows, he finds himself at zero point, where he must completely reset his life to build it up from scratch.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3024,"vote_count":32,"poster_path":"/pMmedMqnkFSpkx5it49TWvg4OcE.jpg","release_date":"2014-12-04","vote_average":7.1,"backdrop_path":"/fFTra41K5kQgowx4TClblrfYZ9.jpg","original_title":"Nullpunkt","original_language":"et"},{"id":5544,"adult":false,"title":"Hiroshima Mon Amour","video":false,"overview":"The deep conversation between a Japanese architect and a French actress forms the basis of this celebrated French film, considered one of the vanguard productions of the French New Wave. Set in Hiroshima after the end of World War II, the couple -- lovers turned friends -- recount, over many hours, previous romances and life experiences. The two intertwine their stories about the past with pondering the devastation wrought by the atomic bomb dropped on the city.","genre_ids":[18,36,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.278,"vote_count":904,"poster_path":"/zieczjWnvalaxwX5EQASEx0on5f.jpg","release_date":"1959-06-10","vote_average":7.685,"backdrop_path":"/4fynFAYPPYCkyIdt0bsCwWn3Hxv.jpg","original_title":"Hiroshima mon amour","original_language":"fr"},{"id":662,"adult":false,"title":"La Jetée","video":false,"overview":"A man confronts his past during an experiment that attempts to find a solution to the problems of a post-apocalyptic world caused by a world war.","genre_ids":[18,10749,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.8858,"vote_count":971,"poster_path":"/elGidsRHXkk8UyrtLbcMhaptDyp.jpg","release_date":"1962-02-16","vote_average":7.883,"backdrop_path":"/3Z2OhNVU0FhxGZJIq6Gn32UNoKu.jpg","original_title":"La Jetée","original_language":"fr"},{"id":113,"adult":false,"title":"Spring, Summer, Fall, Winter... and Spring","video":false,"overview":"An isolated lake, where an old monk lives in a small floating temple. The monk has a young boy living with him, learning to become a monk. We watch as seasons and years pass by.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.7922,"vote_count":1172,"poster_path":"/xw8aVnN6j5zMJSurOI8CEmZZqhU.jpg","release_date":"2003-09-19","vote_average":7.8,"backdrop_path":"/d3Ayxo6kqE1GbNQpqnvElmvkPmm.jpg","original_title":"봄 여름 가을 겨울 그리고 봄","original_language":"ko"},{"id":1092,"adult":false,"title":"The Third Man","video":false,"overview":"In postwar Vienna, Austria, Holly Martins, a writer of pulp Westerns, arrives penniless as a guest of his childhood chum Harry Lime, only to learn he has died. Martins develops a conspiracy theory after learning of a \"third man\" present at the time of Harry's death, running into interference from British officer Major Calloway, and falling head-over-heels for Harry's grief-stricken lover, Anna.","genre_ids":[53,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.5002,"vote_count":2049,"poster_path":"/rO2Fq0AZZx9obs52KJdx4mRE8p5.jpg","release_date":"1949-08-31","vote_average":7.905,"backdrop_path":"/rLLhOCgAjuvlKmjUqVb7P1UAbUI.jpg","original_title":"The Third Man","original_language":"en"},{"id":29264,"adult":false,"title":"The Exterminating Angel","video":false,"overview":"After a lavish dinner party, the guests find themselves unable to depart... and, over the next few days, all of their elaborate societal pretenses and façades deteriorate as they are reduced to living like animals.","genre_ids":[35,18,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3544,"vote_count":715,"poster_path":"/qqZXHvBFxUpo8Pfbyvgh4SYMiWm.jpg","release_date":"1962-05-16","vote_average":7.94,"backdrop_path":"/wJ4HyVZsbZRWH7BS3bLZsvO31rZ.jpg","original_title":"El ángel exterminador","original_language":"es"},{"id":821,"adult":false,"title":"Judgment at Nuremberg","video":false,"overview":"In 1947, four German judges who served on the bench during the Nazi regime face a military tribunal to answer charges of crimes against humanity. Chief Justice Haywood hears evidence and testimony not only from lead defendant Ernst Janning and his defense attorney Hans Rolfe, but also from the widow of a Nazi general, an idealistic U.S. Army captain and reluctant witness Irene Wallner.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.3839,"vote_count":916,"poster_path":"/b6vYatvui1EXeFYfpDX4rcbueuP.jpg","release_date":"1961-12-18","vote_average":8.014,"backdrop_path":"/bDsXa3PV3biQ8ZK1tQyK4vlkvCc.jpg","original_title":"Judgment at Nuremberg","original_language":"en"},{"id":104,"adult":false,"title":"Run Lola Run","video":false,"overview":"Lola receives a phone call from her boyfriend Manni. He lost 100,000 DM in a subway train that belongs to a very bad guy. She has 20 minutes to raise this amount and meet Manni. Otherwise, he will rob a store to get the money. Three different alternatives may happen depending on some minor event along Lola's run.","genre_ids":[28,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.4569,"vote_count":2500,"poster_path":"/v0giIi4bTILVhNhJajet3WWY3FA.jpg","release_date":"1998-08-20","vote_average":7.3,"backdrop_path":"/wRcm3iwi4BeMN59U4fjO7u3dOVI.jpg","original_title":"Lola rennt","original_language":"de"},{"id":4688,"adult":false,"title":"Across the Universe","video":false,"overview":"When young dockworker Jude leaves Liverpool to find his estranged father in the United States, he is swept up by the waves of change that are re-shaping the nation. Jude falls in love with Lucy, who joins the growing anti-war movement. As the body count in Vietnam rises, political tensions at home spiral out of control and the star-crossed lovers find themselves in a psychedelic world gone mad.","genre_ids":[18,10749,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.8326,"vote_count":1414,"poster_path":"/447c8Te3DXC46rQvDEixKGO4dS6.jpg","release_date":"2007-09-14","vote_average":7.1,"backdrop_path":"/sXI5fukqu1Y5sqUk6RaUoW9LJYT.jpg","original_title":"Across the Universe","original_language":"en"},{"id":7735,"adult":false,"title":"The Wave","video":false,"overview":"A school teacher discusses types of government with his class. His students find it too boring to repeatedly go over national socialism and believe that dictatorship cannot be established in modern Germany. He starts an experiment to show how easily the masses can become manipulated.","genre_ids":[18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.8986,"vote_count":3540,"poster_path":"/vtJ4u0fpTZhibxAJHzXtcdCxhsL.jpg","release_date":"2008-03-13","vote_average":7.481,"backdrop_path":"/bxQT6xCjejpGtgKl0QH8WUtrs33.jpg","original_title":"Die Welle","original_language":"de"},{"id":1975,"adult":false,"title":"The Grudge 2","video":false,"overview":"A young woman encounters a malevolent supernatural force while searching for her missing sister in Tokyo, a mean high school prank goes horribly wrong, and strange things begin happening in a Chicago apartment building.","genre_ids":[27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.1178,"vote_count":1100,"poster_path":"/bar7YmgKImN0VljpdLDhvLwMZo4.jpg","release_date":"2006-10-12","vote_average":5.6,"backdrop_path":"/3HTK3FtjK5GXIvPswaIMBMHeL3E.jpg","original_title":"The Grudge 2","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":48400,"adult":false,"title":"Appointment in Berlin","video":false,"overview":"The \"war of nerves\" which gripped the European continent in 1938, is the background for this war thriller starring George Sanders.","genre_ids":[18,10752],"popularity":0.4748,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/k8lPmqroJhmuMZMyKLkJCmCHRO0.jpg","release_date":"1943-07-15","vote_average":6.7,"backdrop_path":"/yQK3FneJNMXVWolSDKuBVKvBiLc.jpg","original_title":"Appointment in Berlin","original_language":"en"},{"id":48751,"adult":false,"title":"Deep Gold","video":false,"overview":"Amy Sanchez (Bebe Pham) is a champion free diver who breaks a crucial free diving record. Her boyfriend, Tony dela Cruz (Jack Prinya), an Air Force Pilot, mysteriously disappears along with his plane that carries gold worth millions of dollars that was to be taken to the Central Bank.  Determined to unearth the truth, she goes off to find out what has actually happened accompanied by her sister Jess Sanchez (Jaymee Ong). She moves on her adventurous journey not knowing that she herself is going to get entangled into a trap of lies that leads her to a much complex conspiracy.","genre_ids":[28,53],"popularity":0.1822,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/4eCQoTJ3QXDxBlXChlc7cF909WO.jpg","release_date":"2011-04-22","vote_average":4.8,"backdrop_path":"/wt7msKHtebDdoDr8tvzELwotJqs.jpg","original_title":"Deep Gold","original_language":"en"},{"id":48753,"adult":false,"title":"Cannibal","video":false,"overview":"Cannibal is based on the true-crime story of Armin Meiwes, the \"Rotenburg Cannibal\" who posted an online ad searching for someone to volunteer to be mutilated and eaten. Unlikely as it may seem, someone actually replied. The film shows a fictional portrayal of the meeting between the cannibal and his victim/participant, their homosexual relationship, and the eventual mutilation and murder of said victim.","genre_ids":[18,27,53,80],"popularity":2.5709,"vote_count":47,"poster_path":"/8BirIrKffS6JvBS55wwA1jX4SlW.jpg","release_date":"2006-12-05","vote_average":5.1,"backdrop_path":"/62rGPICStsCJiH1Tmu5G8UjLR4Y.jpg","original_title":"Cannibal","original_language":"de"},{"id":48764,"adult":false,"title":"The Trial of Joan of Arc","video":false,"overview":"Rouen, Normandy, 1431, during the Hundred Years' War. After being captured by French soldiers from an opposing faction, Joan of Arc, the Maid of Orléans, is unjustly tried by an ecclesiastical court overseen by her English enemies.","genre_ids":[18,36],"popularity":0.3783,"vote_count":147,"poster_path":"/gHb9UUow3j25sMCb3wDIZatfIg1.jpg","release_date":"1963-02-13","vote_average":7.19,"backdrop_path":"/kpjWEZvoMhiinhDArNJ31VXvgh5.jpg","original_title":"Procès de Jeanne d'Arc","original_language":"fr"},{"id":49009,"adult":false,"title":"The Way Back","video":false,"overview":"A small band of multicultural convicts stages a daring escape from a WWII-era Siberian gulag, and embarks on a treacherous journey across five countries in a desperate race for freedom and survival.","genre_ids":[18,12,36],"popularity":2.5382,"vote_count":1716,"poster_path":"/xQ6hxfpD5XQGJz0ekVle5zegam7.jpg","release_date":"2010-11-22","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/jcQfgcq1j7Vit4wQ54niXiLfvE8.jpg","original_title":"The Way Back","original_language":"en"},{"id":49028,"adult":false,"title":"Rakht Charitra","video":false,"overview":"Based on the life of Paritala Ravindra, the film follows his life from just a college student to being a politician in the state of Andhra Pradesh.","genre_ids":[28,80,18],"popularity":0.3286,"vote_count":24,"poster_path":"/cPFW3LMUKUNfj5jaPJVPXZP5U06.jpg","release_date":"2010-10-21","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/wniroOh9ZfNOrcdbS9pCHOTt5a6.jpg","original_title":"रखता चरित्र","original_language":"hi"},{"id":49040,"adult":false,"title":"The Bourne Legacy","video":false,"overview":"New CIA operative Aaron Cross experiences life-or-death stakes that have been triggered by the previous actions of Jason Bourne.","genre_ids":[28,53],"popularity":6.9134,"vote_count":6016,"poster_path":"/1aExL5DTGHj25ZfIC3dDwS84RWi.jpg","release_date":"2012-08-08","vote_average":6.239,"backdrop_path":"/akNBILfG0vh7WhuzjA1bXfrgpYI.jpg","original_title":"The Bourne Legacy","original_language":"en"},{"id":1297860,"adult":false,"title":"Inheritance","video":false,"overview":"When Maya learns her father Sam was once a spy, she suddenly finds herself at the center of an international conspiracy. As she seeks answers, Maya herself becomes a target and must quickly learn the skills of her father.","genre_ids":[53],"popularity":1.6992,"vote_count":71,"poster_path":"/aZGpn6GTtLFkkJ0LmeHtifL1Jw8.jpg","release_date":"2025-01-24","vote_average":5.937,"backdrop_path":"/fuRRTlFH4qazNjUSAmnmGMyNq29.jpg","original_title":"Inheritance","original_language":"en"},{"id":48926,"adult":false,"title":"Sangam","video":false,"overview":"An air force pilot, upon returning home from war after being assumed dead, weds the woman he had long loved, unaware that she had been planning to marry his best friend.","genre_ids":[10749,18,10402],"popularity":0.5621,"vote_count":18,"poster_path":"/kSTQfpeRgubMad65TYbZjmHjrrk.jpg","release_date":"1964-06-18","vote_average":7.3,"backdrop_path":"/bOwjgqQYgh8tkWanOecPIiE79Ks.jpg","original_title":"संगम","original_language":"hi"},{"id":901251,"adult":false,"title":"Rose","video":false,"overview":"Over the course of a week, sisters Inger and Ellen find their relationship challenged on a highly anticipated coach trip to Paris. Inger reveals her struggles with schizophrenia to the group, receiving both pity and discrimination. On arrival, it soon becomes clear that Inger has a hidden agenda concerning a figure from her past, ultimately involving the entire group in her hunt for answers.","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":0.4226,"vote_count":32,"poster_path":"/ewzE98Ajsk92rZQIxAOUHFLIJku.jpg","release_date":"2022-02-24","vote_average":7.7,"backdrop_path":"/tlaVzavuphwLHEgHCxzc1Fn3Z5S.jpg","original_title":"Rose","original_language":"da"},{"id":1298366,"adult":false,"title":"Opfer der Gesellschaft","video":false,"overview":"A prosecutor, keen on punishing those he deems undesirable, convicts a woman of murder. It is only after the conviction that he learns of the circumstances that lead to the crime.","genre_ids":[18,80],"popularity":0.1276,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"1919-01-01","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Opfer der Gesellschaft","original_language":"de"},{"id":1109951,"adult":false,"title":"The Silence Between Two Songs","video":false,"overview":"Laura and Lucas live temporarily in Berlin and are set to go back to Lisbon together soon. I guess this is how I think about myself too. That I will go back to Lisbon soon. But I often find myself doubting it and becoming a kind of split self. Because now with this crisis and the very controversial austerity IMF program running in Portugal I found most of my friends leaving Lisbon; and family about to mortgage their homes. I wanted to talk about this feeling of separation that I see in my generation, about this state of being in between an apparent solid past and an unknown future, about this identity in transition.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.1279,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/4LdINzzi9QcwlI0mbe9RLOhJr32.jpg","release_date":"2013-01-01","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"O silêncio entre duas canções","original_language":"pt"},{"id":49341,"adult":false,"title":"Exhibit A","video":false,"overview":"Exhibit A tells the timely story of a normal family disintegrating under financial pressure. All is not as it seems as the King family go about their day-to-day lives oblivious of the horror to come. Dad Andy (Bradley Cole) is nursing a secret that ultimately leads to terrible consequences for them all. We witness these chilling events unfold through daughter Judith's video camera, which subsequently becomes Exhibit A.","genre_ids":[53,18,80],"popularity":0.2387,"vote_count":65,"poster_path":"/2rh0TE5qEKZ6LuIDSOEvU8jA7YT.jpg","release_date":"2007-10-01","vote_average":5.6,"backdrop_path":"/ne6QvgV5qzc7XfxGJ3PQFihHTa5.jpg","original_title":"Exhibit A","original_language":"en"},{"id":314389,"adult":false,"title":"Baby","video":false,"overview":"A nascent elite team of the Indian intelligence system perpetually strives to detect and eliminate terrorists and their plots. Officer Ajay leads his team to destroy one such potentially lethal ploy in their biggest operation yet.","genre_ids":[28,53],"popularity":2.0493,"vote_count":186,"poster_path":"/5yezGgo37qmd6kDknZKFzbhT19b.jpg","release_date":"2015-01-23","vote_average":6.817,"backdrop_path":"/w94ZL3AcTZpebSLyhKuYfdeeuV6.jpg","original_title":"Baby","original_language":"hi"},{"id":49769,"adult":false,"title":"Don't Let Them Shoot the Kite","video":false,"overview":"Sent to prison along with his mother after her drug conviction, a young boy develops a warm, tender relationship with a political prisoner.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.3932,"vote_count":70,"poster_path":"/oEiAfij9usfev6rSWoKi9dsjRyD.jpg","release_date":"1989-04-14","vote_average":7.9,"backdrop_path":"/dEQeZ1dfX5tkE8XPV8fx681UTn7.jpg","original_title":"Uçurtmayı Vurmasınlar","original_language":"tr"},{"id":1502956,"adult":false,"title":"Triggers","video":false,"overview":"A miserable office worker receives a mysterious package in the mail, and the consequences are more than what most had bargained for.","genre_ids":[53,18],"popularity":0.1284,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/lp59TImA7uoY4NyQmkOHUYQQGyp.jpg","release_date":"2025-04-04","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Triggers","original_language":"en"},{"id":49517,"adult":false,"title":"Tinker Tailor Soldier Spy","video":false,"overview":"In the bleak days of the Cold War, espionage veteran George Smiley is forced from semi-retirement to uncover a Soviet mole within his former colleagues at the heart of MI6.","genre_ids":[18,53,9648],"popularity":3.5452,"vote_count":2855,"poster_path":"/e0dZ7TapGY9HtJ9xk1TUHPEOccl.jpg","release_date":"2011-09-16","vote_average":6.625,"backdrop_path":"/6ZwscHN0bSIueTVTo6mlTGUUP90.jpg","original_title":"Tinker Tailor Soldier Spy","original_language":"en"},{"id":49576,"adult":false,"title":"Adult Children","video":false,"overview":"Anatoli Kuzmich retired and received a separate apartment in a new house. He and his wife are happy and make bright plans for the future: how they will go to theaters, museums, read their favorite books.  But their daughter Lyusya suddenly gets married. Not wanting to part with her, Korolyovs persuade the young spouses to live with them in a new apartment. Soon a child is born, and gradually life together becomes unbearable...","genre_ids":[35,18],"popularity":0.221,"vote_count":6,"poster_path":"/uz8CXtj3AGv9lB5xoQVKCzv15UR.jpg","release_date":"1961-12-06","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/syMpxAnYCrUcSEFNNXR8a2vOcEE.jpg","original_title":"Взрослые дети","original_language":"ru"},{"id":49526,"adult":false,"title":"Premium Rush","video":false,"overview":"In Manhattan, a bike messenger picks up an envelope that attracts the interest of a dirty cop, who pursues the cyclist throughout the city.","genre_ids":[80,28,53],"popularity":2.4063,"vote_count":2242,"poster_path":"/gHnGhJmE0LByOd4RS2mOASmUqQu.jpg","release_date":"2012-08-24","vote_average":6.335,"backdrop_path":"/3QASddh2WWVo9ie2GqivuEXQ8sh.jpg","original_title":"Premium Rush","original_language":"en"},{"id":514708,"adult":false,"title":"The Humorist","video":false,"overview":"The Humorist is a film about a week in the life of Boris Arkadiev, a fictional